'''Kete nectar''' was a rich liquid that was prized for its use in [[Ewok/Legends|Ewok]] potions. The substance was produced the [[Kete]]s in their [[Kete hive|hive]] on the [[Endor/Legends|forest moon of Endor]]. The nectar was carried in small round containers known as [[nectar pearl]]s which allowed the Ketes to easily stock the nectar within various storehouses inside the hive. Kete nectar was known for its use in the antidote to the powerful [[plant growth formula]], and during the [[stranglethorn crisis]], the two Ewoks, [[Kneesaa a Jari Kintaka/Legends|Kneesaa a Jari Kintaka]] and [[Wicket Wystri Warrick/Legends|Wicket Wystri Warrick]] came to the Kete hive to obtain some of the prized nectar. It is unknown if this nectar was used as the source for [[Honey/Legends|honey]].

